build_orders.title: Forest Nothing (Huns)
build_orders.description: A Build Order for Forest Nothing played as Huns. Huns don't need houses making them a perfect civ for this map because of the lack of space. They do lack Siege Onagers however, requiring Trebs for cutting roads between allies. At the start assign a 'cutter' who will make these paths. A good alternative civ for this is Celts, since they have Siege Onagers.

queue.title: Mill on 3x3 Space (5/5)
queue.description: Build a Mill in the Bottom Right 3x3 area.

queue.title: Delete Mill, Build Farm
queue.description: When the Mill is done, delete it. We unlocked farms and reclaim the Mill space with a Farm.

queue.title: 6 Vils->Upper Right 3x3 Area
queue.description: With one Vil on the Farm

queue.title: Start Building Vils->Wood
queue.description: When you reached 50 food immediately queue a vil. Continue cutting 3x3 areas close to the TC.

queue.title: Second Farm
queue.description: You get the idea, keep doing this.
Make sure you have a Mill and Lumbercamp then go up. Communicate with your team to pinpoint the exact time to go up.
